==Description==
The '''Zap Plate''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The Zap Plate has a value of 100 [[Gems|Electric Gems]] {{Gem|Electric}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals.

==Acquisition==
Zap Plates can be found in the [[Underground]], traded for with the [[Berry Master|Hoenn Berry Master]], and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

